{
  "texts": [
    "Zagidullin et al.",
    "proposed an approach where genetic and drug data are used to predict drug combination synergy scores.",
    "Genetic data informs about cancer cell lines, while drug data include molecular structures.",
    "The model employs GAE to encode drug structures, yielding synergy predictions.",
    "While this work focused solely on comparing fingerprint types, future research could explore combining molecular structure or investigating other molecular features."
  ]
}